data.text: @MichaelSFuhrer Yup, it will be a tight race there and probably will depend on non covid deaths

@mikebros Partly taking the piss, and partly serious. You've been able to keep covid out longer, hence vax better than almost anywhere that kept it out. So CFR will be low even after the omicron wave.
@DrPieterPeach There's a bit of taking the piss here, but I think that ultimately this is a good metric (not the only one). No place will keep covid out forever.
@MichaelSFuhrer Might have more to do with the denominator going up than good policies and treatments keeping the numerator down.
@MichaelSFuhrer Only because we've had a shit load of cases in the last few days. But you know that 🙂
@MichaelSFuhrer Just like the bloody All Blacks, always finding a way to win.
